Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:14.03,ShowTitle,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(321,1)}Interviews with Monster Girls
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.39,0:01:34.44,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for taking the time to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:34.44,TakanashiD,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Takanashi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.91,0:01:37.03,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,My daughters have told me about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.89,0:01:40.37,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,and I was hoping for a chance to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:43.04,Title1,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(487,521)}The Takanashi Sisters Are Undeniable
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.90,0:01:42.99,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... I'm the one who's grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:45.50,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for inviting me over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:48.31,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,My wife is the bread winner in our family,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.31,0:01:51.25,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm in charge of the housework.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:53.17,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:01:56.34,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,At one time, both of us had jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:02:00.61,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,But since we have Hikari, we thought \None of us should stay near her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.15,0:02:07.41,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, we've been in touch with Machi-san \Nand Kusakabe-san's parents, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.41,0:02:11.31,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Networking among parents, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:12.52,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,That does sound nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:17.48,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it was thanks to your help \Nthat those girls became friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:20.46,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I didn't do anything special.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:24.37,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing there's someone like you, \Nwho's knowledgeable about demis,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:27.83,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,makes me feel at ease \Nsending them to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:31.02,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Hikari-san and Himari-san \Nhave such good sense
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.02,0:02:34.21,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,because they had good parents \Nto raise them right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:36.84,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari-san, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:42.87,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I just wish she'd put a little \Nmore effort into her studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.33,0:02:44.80,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:48.35,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Himari is very responsible about that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:50.42,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.09,0:02:52.05,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:53.11,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Himari.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:55.38,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:02:57.08,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I did promise, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:02:58.36,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:02.85,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,And... I'm sorry about the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.85,0:03:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.65,0:03:05.46,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,About the e-mail my sister sent me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:07.31,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,The one that said you hugged her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:08.12,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hugged?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:11.38,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that?! It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:14.08,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari explained everything later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:16.59,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,As long as the misunderstanding \Nwas cleared up, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:19.17,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of person my sister is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:24.56,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,You have my blessing to be \Nstrict and not coddle her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.56,0:03:25.46,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:31.25,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:35.17,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,They're twins, but they're \Ncompletely different...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:36.44,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sor—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:38.30,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:40.26,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:41.28,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,There, she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:42.07,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:45.02,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here? A home visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:46.89,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to talk to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I asked him over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:50.57,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:53.58,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:56.03,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, you're wearing a necktie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.03,0:03:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unusual!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:59.33,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can I take a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:00.57,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Click, click—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:01.63,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.77,0:04:04.13,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,H-Himari?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.38,0:04:07.81,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,You put your blood pack in this fridge again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:11.20,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Keep them in your own fridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:14.27,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You have your own refrigerator?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:18.80,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it seemed wrong to put my blood \Nwhere everyone would see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:19.98,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,so I got my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:23.46,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't even matter. \NWe're used to seeing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:24.72,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:27.56,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,But the deal was that, as long \Nas you had your own fridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd follow the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:32.42,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably something foolish, \Nlike you couldn't be bothered
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.42,0:04:34.10,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,to take them upstairs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:39.62,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, please say something to this \Ncold-blooded sister of mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:42.77,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,It's important to question the rules,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.77,0:04:46.66,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,but you should really stick to rules \Nthat you set for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:50.67,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,The gentle way he worded that \Nstabs right through my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:52.62,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Just listen to this, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:55.94,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,She does what she wants, just because \Nshe has her own fridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:04:59.06,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,She hides the desserts she wants to eat in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:02.07,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,sticks her feet in it while reading manga,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:06.81,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,and worst, sleeps with her \Nhead in it and gets sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:08.69,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:10.37,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,D-Did you have to say all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're making the blood drain from my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:16.35,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Himari, say another word, and you'll regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:18.13,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,What? Want to fight me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.37,0:05:22.79,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,When we were kids, we used to \Nhit each other all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:24.33,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It makes my blood boil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.33,0:05:26.18,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:28.84,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,This is gonna be a bloodbath!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.94,0:05:34.71,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you keep working in \Nidioms that involve blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:37.37,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Since I have the chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd let Sensei and Dad \Nsee my vampire intelligence—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:45.26,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,You always try too hard to \Nmake yourself look good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:50.26,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is with this hairstyle that \Ntakes so maddeningly long to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:50.26,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:53.89,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see why you have to bring up my hair—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:53.89,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,But I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:57.81,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how often helping you \Nwith your hair has made me late?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:58.62,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ow! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:02.65,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, say something to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:03.17,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:06.97,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I think that hairstyle looks pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:17.58,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:19.01,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is red.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.01,0:06:20.81,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:21.64,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:22.82,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:24.77,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,That's a problem for me, as it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:25.95,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,How is it a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,0:06:27.68,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Are they always like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:28.48,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:30.91,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm embarrassed to say it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:33.43,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,but they make such a fuss, \NI don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:34.79,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:38.12,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,It's clear they're very close, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:40.33,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:42.63,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way, Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:47.42,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have plans after this, \Nwould you care to stay for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:50.12,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,What? Wow, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:51.85,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I'd appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:53.06,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:55.64,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei is having dinner with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:57.01,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:06:58.93,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Liver and onions!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:06:58.93,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Liver and on—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:10.69,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand your liking \Nliver and onions, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:12.80,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:17.20,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Himari's short on blood \Nbecause she's always so angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:19.96,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Say something to her, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:23.32,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Can't fight what's in your blood, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:25.43,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, not you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:31.41,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Sensei... Make a good face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:32.84,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You just took a picture earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:35.01,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But not one with us together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:36.51,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta send it to Macchi and Yukki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:41.21,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, you could at least settle \Ndown a little while Sensei's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:42.85,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you want in the picture, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:45.11,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Wha? I never said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:46.61,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.22,0:07:49.75,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds awfully loud in here... Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:52.00,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, pardon my intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:53.40,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,This is Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:54.91,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. I'm Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:58.29,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my daughters always talk about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:08:00.86,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like you've done \Na great deal for Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:02.33,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:04.25,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:06.37,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.37,0:08:07.93,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:10.43,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,You ate the ice cream I was saving, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.43,0:08:13.22,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I ate it by mistake yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.49,0:08:14.97,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do that by mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:18.66,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe I'd bought it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:21.14,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,You know that'd never actually happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:22.56,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.39,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,You said that the last time you ate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:26.86,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, they're always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.33,0:08:31.43,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since she was born, Hikari's hair \Nhas been so bright, it seems to glow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:33.95,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's why you named her "Hikari"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:36.10,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,As for Himari,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we wanted to give her a \Nname similar to "Hikari."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.61,0:08:39.79,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:44.71,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure there's still \None left in my fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:47.49,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,If you have your own, don't eat mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:49.55,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, it was a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:55.05,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,She may be a vampire, but she isn't \Nthat different from other girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:58.35,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,At least, I used to say that to \Nmake light of the situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:09:02.77,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'd be lying if I said \NI never felt troubled by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:04.27,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,If we face it together,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.72,0:09:10.37,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,we can think of it as part of \Nwhat makes her unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:12.06,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Even besides being a demi,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no two people are the same, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:18.06,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.06,0:09:21.86,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari-san and Himari-san may look similar,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.86,0:09:23.43,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,but see how different they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.43,0:09:25.52,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:27.75,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,How could you forget you ate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:30.66,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'll go buy a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:33.42,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, sure. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:38.64,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So on that note, we're going to buy \Nice cream at the convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:39.89,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,We?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:44.74,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be worried, letting my precious \Nlittle sister go alone at this hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.74,0:09:46.98,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you assume I'd be the one to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:48.85,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Go by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:50.48,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Hikari, you can go with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:53.12,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,And you don't have to spoil her like that, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:56.03,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,She always goes alone to buy sweets at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:10:00.23,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go. There's something I forgot to buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:01.97,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:03.36,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then I'll just—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:05.16,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sensei, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:08.94,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,We're stepping out for a bit, \Nbut the store is nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:10.40,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be long,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you'll have to excuse us \Nfor just a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.63,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:15.30,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Himari!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep Sensei company.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:19.22,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:19.22,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:20.79,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:24.72,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,See you in a few!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:27.64,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, I'll buy one for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:30.73,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I let the timing slip by.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:33.98,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's so soft on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.39,0:10:36.32,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You two really are close, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:38.65,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.19,0:10:42.30,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad's hair is really light in color.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.30,0:10:43.37,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Does he...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:47.36,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, so that Onee-chan won't be too \Nconspicuous within our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:49.71,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? That's really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:54.67,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it looks like you've lightened \Nyour hair a little, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:11:00.55,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! Th-This is just... for fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:06.54,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,They really are close.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:10.24,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mom, what did you forget to buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.24,0:11:11.05,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:13.62,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei looks like a drinker, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:16.94,Eyecatch,,0000,0000,0000,,Interviews with Monster Girls
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:18.94,TakanashiN,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Takanashi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:22.51,Default - flashback,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going now—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:24.03,Default - flashback,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Himari!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.47,0:11:26.20,Default - flashback,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:29.23,Default - flashback,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,First, help me with my hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.21,Default - flashback,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:45.84,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how I forced my sister \Nto become more independent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:48.21,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You're so harsh, Himari-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:51.12,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I can just picture Hikari's face \Nwhen you said that to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:53.23,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,She's just too negligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:54.81,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,She's in high school now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has to get it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.89,0:11:58.28,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Not long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She went to the bathroom at night, \Nand then fell asleep there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:03.29,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.81,0:12:09.33,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but don't you think being a vampire \Nhad something to do with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:12.85,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Vampires can get by in the middle \Nof the night, without any light.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:13.73,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,In fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.73,0:12:16.53,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, when she uses the bathroom at night,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the light's too bright for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:22.50,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,For anyone else, that would make \Nit a lot easier to fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.83,0:12:27.26,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Even considering that, I think her \Nnegligence comes out on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:30.51,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,And what you said a minute ago,\N about her hairstyle...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:34.05,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,That might have something to do \Nwith her vampire nature, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:34.73,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.05,0:12:38.59,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Here, look. Vampires don't see \Ntheir reflections in mirrors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:43.45,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Since they can't see themselves, \Ndoing their own hair is difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:45.52,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she relies on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:48.27,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,That would explain things, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.27,0:12:50.24,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's probably a superstition, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:54.58,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,It's based on a belief that the link between \Na vampire's body and soul is weak,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:57.46,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,or that mirrors reflect the soul, \Nor things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:13:00.38,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I figure it's just because \NHikari is irresponsib—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:02.79,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Himari-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:06.76,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,I might have done something really awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.23,0:13:10.89,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,H-Himari-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:15.77,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,If vampires really can't see \Nthemselves in mirrors...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:20.02,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,If Onee-chan was actually \Nasking for my help...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:20.82,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:27.78,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's going to rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:29.87,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,It's supposed to rain this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:31.62,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to call for a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:32.59,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,A ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.59,0:13:36.02,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, walking around with an umbrella is dangerous for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:39.66,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,So when it rains, I have someone \Nin my family drive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:41.32,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:44.17,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Himari-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:45.67,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:48.09,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:50.28,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if you're looking for Hikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:54.63,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.09,0:13:57.44,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I didn't realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.93,0:14:00.24,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,I just decided that you were negligent,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:01.82,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,and acted like I knew everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:06.95,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you were going \Nthrough so much worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:09.52,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me apologize, Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:12.98,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Mirrors?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:14.80,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I can see myself in them just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:19.84,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Sorry, Himari-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:22.21,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,This happened because I gave \Nyou that weird idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:24.13,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:26.49,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,I was jumping to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:27.80,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:30.21,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, when you do my hair for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.21,0:14:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can also see me in the mirror, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.03,0:14:34.51,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,That's true... That really is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:38.95,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I guess I really worried you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:41.78,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a kind girl, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:45.03,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You can't help jumping to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:49.57,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I made you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:52.45,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Himari.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.86,0:14:57.81,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why make me help with your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:14:58.62,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:01.21,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:04.75,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I am, and always have been, \Njust that negligent!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:09.38,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts! My brains are gonna pop out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:10.09,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:16.93,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Even if vampires didn't cast \Nreflections in mirrors,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:19.35,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari would never lose who she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:21.49,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:23.08,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Himari-chan, who understands \Nand cares for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:25.61,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,is always closer to her than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:26.68,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:30.10,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Onee-chan! You left this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:32.39,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it to the classroom with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:36.91,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to carry it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:41.37,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,She's the perfect younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.40,0:15:56.68,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It really did start raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.90,0:15:58.70,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bring an umbrella?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:01.60,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm fine. I have a folding one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.11,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:08.82,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:12.29,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm gonna head home first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:14.25,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,All right. See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:17.67,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:21.97,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,That staff meeting ran long, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:23.12,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,It sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:27.02,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'm here till late, either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:27.92,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Until late?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:31.42,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I mean, crowded trains are a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.94,0:16:33.76,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm a succubus and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:35.33,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the aphrodisi—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:38.47,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, yeah, that's rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:41.01,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:45.65,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:50.65,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:51.28,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.98,0:16:55.11,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. Have a good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.37,0:16:58.82,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. Same to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.66,0:17:08.04,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,The aphrodisiac effect really \Ndoesn't work on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.64,0:17:12.05,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,If it's him, even a succubus like me could...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:15.87,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,, she's erotic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:18.09,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,It's raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:20.51,BioRoom,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Biology Prep Room
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.51,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Which means she's probably here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:23.39,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't hear anything, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:25.95,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,So maybe she's in the library?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.41,0:17:30.52,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,She's asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:10.98,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops, I fell asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:14.28,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,A blanket?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:41.81,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, that's a good boy. Just sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:08.95,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei's hair is so coarse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.95,0:19:11.88,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Our hairstyles are similar, \Nbut the hair is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:23.51,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:25.22,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Kyouko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I keep you waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:28.39,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari-chan's dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:29.76,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:31.28,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:31.98,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:34.90,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I e-mailed Hikari. She didn't tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:35.65,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:40.60,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It seems both your parents are really busy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:42.03,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,so I came for you instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:43.90,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.90,0:19:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the e-mail, I told her to \Nlet you know in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:49.09,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.09,0:19:51.71,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,right before she left, she had \Na funny smirk on her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:55.36,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She must have kept it to herself, as a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:56.71,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that, Kyouko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:20:00.73,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's all right. Sorry to trouble you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:03.30,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It's no trouble whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:06.79,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I owe your parents a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.08,0:20:09.35,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,As they say, it's give and take.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:10.99,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.99,0:20:13.01,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Takahashi-sensei is worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.01,0:20:14.60,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,It seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:17.89,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Then, want to leave him \Na note before we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.89,0:20:18.89,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:23.85,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I left my backpack in the classroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:25.90,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.77,0:20:31.25,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'll carry your head \Nto the classroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:34.51,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? B-But I couldn't ask that of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:38.50,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I wanted to get used to carrying \Nyou, without shaking you too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:40.46,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:42.17,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:44.88,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't keep trying, over and over,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll never master it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.40,0:20:47.80,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, so smooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.24,0:20:50.82,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'll walk a little slowly. Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:52.15,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:59.41,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably better at that than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:02.61,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that's over wi—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:03.28,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.84,0:21:06.44,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot her body was still here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:08.87,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,She's writing a note?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:20.34,Writing,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi-sensei, \NMy ride is here, so I'll be leaving. \NHikari-chan's dad came to pick me up today. \NAlso, thank you for the blanket. \NIt was very warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:24.34,Writing,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26}It was very warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.87,0:21:26.88,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,She's so serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:31.53,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Still, it takes some skill to be \Nable to write without seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:34.26,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,She must have practiced a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.86,0:21:38.90,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Machi and all the demi-chans \Nare doing their best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.20,0:21:43.32,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Their parents are doing their best for \Ntheir demi-chan daughters, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.05,0:21:45.53,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I need to do more, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:03.87,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I guess, sometimes, it's also \Nnice to say nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.93,0:23:39.94,Title2,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time \NSuccubus-san Is Inquisitive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.67,0:23:37.93,Default,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Next time on {\i1}Interviews with Monster Girls:{\i0}
